The London Sessions is the thirteenth studio album by American R&B recording artist Mary J. Blige. It was released on November 24, 2014 by Capitol Records. Blige says that the London influence - and the contribution of her young collaborators - has created a whole new synthesis for her music, with an album that encompasses both heartfelt soul and thunking dance tunes, all of which show off the performer's rich vocals
